<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Review Notification</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>New Review on Your Course: <%= courseTitle %></h2>
    <p>Dear Course Owner,</p>
    <p>
      A new review has been posted on your course "<%= courseTitle %>".
    </p>
    <p><strong>Rating:</strong> <%= reviewRating %></p>
    <p><strong>Review:</strong> <%= reviewContent %></p>
    <p><strong>Review from:</strong> <%= reviewingUser %></p>
    <p>Best regards,<br />Your E-learning Platform Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
